      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Key activities include\nmanaging the online\nplatform, maintaining\ninventory, processing\ncustomer orders,\nmarketing and promotion,\nmanaging supplier\nrelationships with\npublishers, and handling\ndelivery and logistics.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Key activities include managing the online platform, maintaining inventory, processing customer orders, marketing and promotion, managing supplier relationships with publishers, and handling delivery and logistics.",
